{"tid":229664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊奈良   外國遊客遭鹿攻擊   87％為中國人","createTime":"2017-05-04T17:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T13:42:43.000Z","uid":62257,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40411fdb29e1d6ef052c6258605d4d8919056b94","tid":229664,"uid":62257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:33:28.000Z","msg":"好有靈性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2056019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2056019&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItTzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=19beeead\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2056019&h=5a23d372\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2056019</a><br />\n遊奈良小心！外國遊客遭鹿攻擊 87％為中國人<br />\n2017-05-03 20:56<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕許多台灣人都喜歡到日本旅遊，有不少人更是把前往奈良餵鹿列為必備行程。近日，日本奈良縣政府統計，2016年外國遊客遭鹿咬傷的人數為88人，且有超過87%為中國人。<br />\n根據日本《每日新聞》報導，日本奈良縣政府統計，2016年於奈良公園被鹿攻擊而受傷的人數高達121人，較前年度多出29人，為史上最高。121人中超過7成、88人為外國人，較2013年度的12人高出7倍以上。大多數是在餵食鹿仙貝時所造成的。<br />\n根據奈良公園事務處所提供的資訊指出，88名外國遊客中有77人為中國人，大多數為輕傷，另外遭鹿強烈撞擊而受傷者共10人、傷口須縫合者為6人、骨折則為1人。<br />\n針對此一狀況奈良政府表示，為防範類似情形劇增，將於公園內多設置告示牌，希望旅客能快樂出門，平安回家。"},{"pid":"8303a67c2430d609863ce5e1870d54f66fc5e828","tid":229664,"uid":6558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9700bb338e7daac7d3c0bb9913581b22588404dd","tid":229664,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:47:29.000Z","msg":"等五毛話小日本乜乜物物"},{"pid":"d66a1cfdb3b71ffc7254fceffbba709d73a07091","tid":229664,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T18:58:18.000Z","msg":"仆街鹿正一法西斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma